Invocation Name: phoenix guide
des:
The ultimate city guide for Pheonix travelers. This skill would give an overview of the city by asking -"Alexa ask Phoenix guide more information about Phoenix". It can also give you the best attractions or top 5 things to do with their address and contact details. You can check your Alexa app for more information about your query. 


Invocation Name: Phoenix Guide
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
